{"tid":104724,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【柏拉圖式】只准扑野禁止打車輪","createTime":"2017-02-02T10:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T04:59:57.000Z","uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54fd5691fef5573ef13ca65bef4365fb3a97416f","tid":104724,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得同條女扑野，但唔比打車輪，成年事好撚高質?<br />\n因為大家都係SP，只係性需要先一齊，打車輪依D要留比自己真正愛既女生!!!<br />\n近排班手足介紹我睇依套H漫，我睇撚到喊左，純愛呀!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://exhentai.org/g/1014811/df2e4bc9ea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexhentai.org%2Fg%2F1014811%2Fdf2e4bc9ea%2F&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=dbf7bb13\" target=\"_blank\">https://exhentai.org/g/1014811/df2e4bc9ea/</a><br />\n<br />\n講咁多其實想尋另一套H漫，內容係講一個姐姐+正太<br />\n兩個係青梅竹馬，正太知道姐姐做過援交，正太拎左豬仔錢箱話想買佢身體一屌<br />\n結果兩個做左愛，但姐姐唔比正太同佢打車輪，因為姐姐話 : 打車輪要留比將來愛既女生<br />\n嘩!!!!!!!!!成件事高質到!!!!!!!!有無人可以比番條H漫我?想收藏!<br />\n我希望全世界都可以 &quot;扑野為性，打車輪為真愛，這個前題而生存!!!&quot;"},{"pid":"79491d00278c3cbf85206cbce5c0126c683c8f65","tid":104724,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://emojipedia-us.s3.amazonaws.com/cache/57/9f/579f4ac195f9ccf3cb49c12edb8835ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Femojipedia-us.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcache%2F57%2F9f%2F579f4ac195f9ccf3cb49c12edb8835ef.png&h=afc06997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29ef9839f2bf301ffac38f95e0a9ae31728bdac8","tid":104724,"uid":31429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd00ac1fa691ae346a0751aa3d6f3989a24ad6b","tid":104724,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"(C88) [Otaku Beam (Ootsuka Mahiro)] Stay by Me"},{"pid":"59bc71aa51bd46258178f877e6843e8262749767","tid":104724,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,